[{"text": "Have you ever heard of something called", "start": 0.0, "duration": 1.968}, {"text": "water fasting?", "start": 1.968, "duration": 1.869}, {"text": "Well, it\u2019s a type of fast", "start": 3.837, "duration": 2.302}, {"text": "that restricts everything", "start": 6.139, "duration": 2.102}, {"text": "except, well, water.", "start": 8.241, "duration": 3.003}, {"text": "Most people only water fast", "start": 11.244, "duration": 1.869}, {"text": "for 72 hours at most,", "start": 13.113, "duration": 2.335}, {"text": "but what if you did this", "start": 15.448, "duration": 2.836}, {"text": "for the rest of your life?", "start": 18.284, "duration": 2.536}, {"text": "You\u2019d be fine, right?", "start": 20.82, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "Haha, yeah, not so much.", "start": 23.456, "duration": 4.638}, {"text": "Hey, water is pretty important.", "start": 47.313, "duration": 3.237}, {"text": "And when I say pretty important,", "start": 50.55, "duration": 2.102}, {"text": "I mean absolutely essential.", "start": 52.652, "duration": 3.904}, {"text": "Your own body is 60% water.", "start": 56.556, "duration": 3.637}, {"text": "That\u2019s a big chunk if you ask me.", "start": 60.193, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "Now, drinking water", "start": 62.996, "duration": 1.568}, {"text": "can have some pretty big perks.", "start": 64.564, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "It can lower the risk of heart disease,", "start": 67.2, "duration": 2.269}, {"text": " diabetes and even certain cancers.", "start": 69.469, "duration": 3.737}, {"text": "It sounds great, right?", "start": 73.206, "duration": 1.902}, {"text": "Well, do you think you could try", "start": 75.108, "duration": 1.835}, {"text": "this water-only diet?", "start": 76.943, "duration": 1.602}, {"text": "You could?", "start": 78.545, "duration": 0.901}, {"text": "Well, hey,", "start": 79.446, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "I love your energy,", "start": 80.613, "duration": 1.535}, {"text": "but I\u2019ve got some bad news.", "start": 82.148, "duration": 2.236}, {"text": "You\u2019ve got 70 days.", "start": 84.384, "duration": 2.202}, {"text": "Tops.", "start": 86.586, "duration": 2.469}, {"text": "You start your water-only diet", "start": 90.323, "duration": 2.202}, {"text": " and you\u2019d be feeling OK.", "start": 92.525, "duration": 2.102}, {"text": "Good even.", "start": 94.627, "duration": 1.669}, {"text": "You\u2019d start to feel hungry and angry,", "start": 97.997, "duration": 3.704}, {"text": "or as the scientific community ", "start": 101.701, "duration": 1.502}, {"text": "calls it, hangry.", "start": 103.203, "duration": 2.335}, {"text": "That\u2019s because your body", "start": 105.538, "duration": 1.569}, {"text": "would be running out", "start": 107.107, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "of its glucose supply.", "start": 107.974, "duration": 2.035}, {"text": "Glucose is your body\u2019s", "start": 110.009, "duration": 2.169}, {"text": "primary energy source,", "start": 112.178, "duration": 1.535}, {"text": "and you stock up on it", "start": 113.713, "duration": 1.602}, {"text": "when you consume carbohydrates.", "start": 115.315, "duration": 2.702}, {"text": "But now that you\u2019ve sworn off food,", "start": 118.017, "duration": 3.37}, {"text": "your body would be", "start": 121.387, "duration": 1.469}, {"text": "frantically searching for its next", "start": 122.856, "duration": 2.168}, {"text": "glucose fix.", "start": 125.024, "duration": 2.069}, {"text": "You could lose 2 kg (4.4 lb) every day.", "start": 128.661, "duration": 4.104}, {"text": "This is due to the one-two punch", "start": 132.765, "duration": 2.036}, {"text": "of dehydration", "start": 134.801, "duration": 1.968}, {"text": "and electrolyte imbalance.", "start": 136.769, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "So what happens next?", "start": 139.572, "duration": 2.603}, {"text": "Your body would have adjusted", "start": 143.91, "duration": 1.768}, {"text": "to the lack of food", "start": 145.678, "duration": 1.101}, {"text": "and would be in a state of ketosis.", "start": 146.779, "duration": 3.037}, {"text": "This is where your body", "start": 149.816, "duration": 1.468}, {"text": "would start breaking down fat for energy", "start": 151.284, "duration": 2.703}, {"text": "instead of glucose.", "start": 153.987, "duration": 2.035}, {"text": "You might even feel a little better, ", "start": 156.022, "duration": 2.603}, {"text": "but don\u2019t be fooled.", "start": 158.625, "duration": 2.402}, {"text": "You\u2019re a hurting unit.", "start": 161.027, "duration": 2.236}, {"text": "Now, the more fat reserves you have,", "start": 163.263, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "the longer you\u2019d survive.", "start": 165.899, "duration": 1.635}, {"text": "But once all your fat is gone,", "start": 167.534, "duration": 3.336}, {"text": "you\u2019d have nothing to break down", "start": 170.87, "duration": 1.602}, {"text": "but muscle.", "start": 172.472, "duration": 1.868}, {"text": "And in case you forgot,", "start": 174.34, "duration": 2.002}, {"text": "your heart is an organ made of muscle.", "start": 176.342, "duration": 3.671}, {"text": "This can be incredibly dangerous.", "start": 180.013, "duration": 3.436}, {"text": "When your heart lacks fuel,", "start": 183.449, "duration": 1.936}, {"text": "your pulse and blood pressure will tank.", "start": 185.385, "duration": 3.57}, {"text": "That\u2019s because you can\u2019t", "start": 188.955, "duration": 1.802}, {"text": "pump blood normally anymore.", "start": 190.757, "duration": 2.135}, {"text": "Your proteins would all be", "start": 192.892, "duration": 1.769}, {"text": "broken down at this point,", "start": 194.661, "duration": 1.635}, {"text": "and you\u2019d be barely able to think.", "start": 196.296, "duration": 2.569}, {"text": "That\u2019s because you\u2019d be starving.", "start": 198.865, "duration": 4.071}, {"text": "Your gastrointestinal system", "start": 204.504, "duration": 1.702}, {"text": "would be wrecked.", "start": 206.206, "duration": 1.835}, {"text": "This would cause stomach pain, ", "start": 208.041, "duration": 2.102}, {"text": "vomiting and, my personal favorite,", "start": 210.143, "duration": 2.969}, {"text": "bacterial infections.", "start": 213.112, "duration": 3.137}, {"text": "Things would be looking even worse.", "start": 217.517, "duration": 3.704}, {"text": "Your body would be", "start": 221.221, "duration": 1.034}, {"text": "in a state of malnutrition,", "start": 222.255, "duration": 1.868}, {"text": "and you\u2019d feel weaker than ever.", "start": 224.123, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "You can look forward", "start": 226.759, "duration": 1.035}, {"text": "to various health problems,", "start": 227.794, "duration": 1.568}, {"text": "like dizziness,", "start": 229.362, "duration": 1.568}, {"text": "headaches and difficulty concentrating.", "start": 230.93, "duration": 3.771}, {"text": "As the days went on, ", "start": 234.701, "duration": 0.767}, {"text": "you\u2019d continue to deteriorate.", "start": 235.468, "duration": 3.637}, {"text": "you\u2019d experience more severe symptoms,", "start": 240.24, "duration": 2.869}, {"text": "such as extreme fatigue,", "start": 243.109, "duration": 2.402}, {"text": "rapid weight loss and muscle wasting.", "start": 245.511, "duration": 3.971}, {"text": "And you\u2019d also have to worry about", "start": 249.482, "duration": 2.035}, {"text": "serious health problems like", "start": 251.517, "duration": 1.969}, {"text": "kidney failure", "start": 253.486, "duration": 1.268}, {"text": "or sepsis.", "start": 254.754, "duration": 2.369}, {"text": "You, uh, you don\u2019t look so good.", "start": 259.192, "duration": 4.004}, {"text": "You\u2019d be extremely weak", "start": 263.196, "duration": 1.868}, {"text": "and unable to do much on your own.", "start": 265.064, "duration": 3.404}, {"text": "You\u2019d also be at ", "start": 268.468, "duration": 0.934}, {"text": "high risk of death from organ failure", "start": 269.402, "duration": 2.603}, {"text": "or infection.", "start": 272.005, "duration": 1.901}, {"text": "Did you know that most people die", "start": 273.906, "duration": 1.736}, {"text": "not from starvation,", "start": 275.642, "duration": 1.735}, {"text": "but from infectious diseases?", "start": 277.377, "duration": 3.203}, {"text": "Yeah, your immune system suffers", "start": 280.58, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "while you\u2019re perpetually starving", "start": 283.383, "duration": 1.935}, {"text": "because of the deficiency", "start": 285.318, "duration": 1.268}, {"text": "of vitamins and minerals.", "start": 286.586, "duration": 2.135}, {"text": "This leaves you open", "start": 288.721, "duration": 1.969}, {"text": "to all sorts of nasty germs.", "start": 290.69, "duration": 2.836}, {"text": "It\u2019s unlikely that you\u2019d survive", "start": 296.929, "duration": 2.403}, {"text": "much longer on a water-only diet.", "start": 299.332, "duration": 3.203}, {"text": "You\u2019d be severely malnourished", "start": 302.535, "duration": 2.269}, {"text": "and reeling from ", "start": 304.804, "duration": 1.435}, {"text": "a greatest-hits compilation", "start": 306.239, "duration": 1.935}, {"text": "of health problems.", "start": 308.174, "duration": 1.201}, {"text": "But hey, you did it!", "start": 309.375, "duration": 3.27}, {"text": "And we\u2019re sending the medics", "start": 312.645, "duration": 1.735}, {"text": "to you right now.", "start": 314.38, "duration": 1.302}, {"text": "Was it worth it?", "start": 315.682, "duration": 2.235}, {"text": "Well, no, not really.", "start": 317.917, "duration": 2.436}, {"text": "A water-only diet", "start": 320.353, "duration": 1.768}, {"text": "is not sustainable in the long term.", "start": 322.121, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "A balanced diet", "start": 324.924, "duration": 1.835}, {"text": "is essential for maintaining", "start": 326.759, "duration": 2.102}, {"text": "good health.", "start": 328.861, "duration": 0.701}, {"text": "It\u2019s kind of fascinating though, right?", "start": 329.562, "duration": 4.037}, {"text": "Despite being on the brink,", "start": 333.599, "duration": 2.136}, {"text": "you still made it to 70 days.", "start": 335.735, "duration": 2.736}, {"text": "If the human body is that resilient,", "start": 338.471, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "what else can we try?", "start": 341.274, "duration": 3.17}, {"text": "Well, what if you only drank ", "start": 344.444, "duration": 2.702}, {"text": "Coca-Cola for a month?", "start": 347.146, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "Well, grab yourself a soda from the fridge,", "start": 349.949, "duration": 3.237}, {"text": "because that\u2019s a story \nfor another WHAT IF. ", "start": 353.186, "duration": 5.305}]